4. The 6 Core =E2=80=9CAgents=E2=80=9D You Actually Need
Forget 10=E2=80=9315 agents. Realtors only need 6:
1. =F0=9F=A7=B2 Lead Response Agent (MOST IMPORTANT)
What it does:
replies to new inquiries in < 1 minute
qualifies buyer/seller
asks structured questions
pushes into CRM
Example behavior:
Incoming message:
=E2=80=9CIs this house still available?=E2=80=9D
Agent replies:
=E2=80=9CYes it is. Are you looking to buy within the next 30=E2=80=9390 da=
ys, and do you
already have financing pre-approved?=E2=80=9D
Then:
tags lead as =E2=80=9Chot / warm / cold=E2=80=9D
stores in CRM
2. =F0=9F=93=9E Follow-up Agent
This is where most deals are won.
Automatically:

follows up every 2=E2=80=937 days
sends personalized messages
revives cold leads
Example:
=E2=80=9CHey John, just checking in=E2=80=94are you still exploring homes i=
n Calgary or are
you on pause for now?=E2=80=9D
This alone can increase conversion massively.
